Class PcmRepositorySeffExtractor

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.uka.ipd.sdq.beagle.core.pcmconnection.PcmRepositorySeffExtractor

  • public class PcmRepositorySeffExtractor
extends Object
    Extractor class for SEFFElements. Adding all EObjects that are SeffLoops, SeffBranches, ResourceDemandingInternalActions or ExternalCallParameters to given sets.

        seffLoopSet - the SeffLoopSet to add SeffLoops
